;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h3 style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 400;"&gt;化石燃料达到顶峰&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;2021年，习近平&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SpTDbm6IAX6ADKvlduk7asn4Nc-MzbGpKPE91RR461HdGOU21tMaZepldfvLhiRGbB68QNWJpdRalpmNjkuRBWQ9wSTSWDIa1DzpvYBG7K39m2GtL5tbX692u20fSXqRcB9NUISjZOqFk5eXCuylOuq7rR8Q6Wp-ZdW2J3y7gXpX95MTqZ08xNgP3m_XW1M_czclBwuZ0F11jzPmdQfE3bABcNoMeOeQSydEqZA19wQ6lPCMe0O-q69-QaW0onyGP3-tar3tVd4YCG6lPr9B0caLMDVKggCG365znPTrXLcgNHNzjs4p6YvG64xofJp1MwwEzGFnR-mR4_Y42qoAXksOpa8JcbE1MtKX/f2PFXqJUMkE6dHzKiFI2uitgTUB7uZKZ/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="习近平在“领导人气候峰会”上的讲话（双语全文）"&gt;呼吁&lt;/a&gt;中国在“十五五”期间开始减少煤炭消费。然而，他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qPLbPbEmedxlEnRh-CWOuFE8UUZGtk8bT5em_2181oMSmmgSTgMdAJYrlv-Bw3kACGQ28UTRsF0cPXwdoVWqrNCmCpzuqhhZpfpvV3Yx5YQwpUSPXAx999FCmRUFYeg5uUjIC3cANTGJp1YC_pTyPV61lt_2_TAnYXkxmEo_QOXrWUNlVlQ833XddhrHnvRV0qNjeebWzCOjojxHpULxPneCKf2gYPt3XxtkEY4JktvDyAVyPqzN_7OkZeoPwALHuzwcCnbiCfazgD5K7JxLyx5giOznXvN-AlPv913TeR-6UaXTzNCrAJOwNWdVmXQfzGgCcQy92bez-oeGt6pUsYf6TvZW/glOtUpOK54eFt8asYgNtRkLla69-wLky/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="当前经济工作的重点任务 - 求是网"&gt;最近&lt;/a&gt;使用了稍微保守的语言——而是呼吁在未来五年内达到峰值，但没有提到任何减少。同样的措辞也出现在第十五个五年计划的提案中。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;五年计划发布后，&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;请阅读&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/yY66CsEGhYklgp6OoQvDEIufrgaMoslH27RcRRVn0Oh5daKRm44MkfrMdb8p0YgTBlTeFGVq3De_jSvKIH_2IlRBJZSoOiPWvxSNrotm27L09-glDs3OY0l8-JCJh418VhXl5dbbgxbZnSQpU71h0gBtXuBg7Qfflgm-k1JAUCLFyEFSGm6YG_X2gHxYngwSDVo2PmWi3j9_PL2p8faqgFoGugxcnDjxtf70544aEMWwy5fPf4HImgUYVJnxlS_Btd7Yoe3RyeW_kXjmRD6tV9IpjActuPhuxqCtFO81qKhcEibHO6i97vTcjEErI_CgQqHPzMBgFHjeVa9TZBTzcjF1dQH4tsa6